<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HE HIDETH MY SOUL</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa mak Isu ka Lalpa ahi,
 Kei dinga Hukdampa mak chuh!
 Ka thagau Suongpi khi kalah A sel hi,
 Zie chun nawpna luiluong ka mu'i.

[V2]
 Ka thagau A sel, suongpi khikal a chun,
 Gamgaw leh gam haksatna ah;
 Ka hinna A sel, A hehpihna thukah,
 * Zie chun A khutin ei lieh hi (2)

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa mak Isu ka Lalpa ahi,
 Ka puokgik cheng A lamang tai;
 Ama'n ei tui, bangmah lau ngei puong ka,
 Nicheng in hatna thak ei pie'i.

[V4]
 3. Vangsak gensen lohin phat chengin ei thuom,
 A phatna'n ei sukipak zing;
 Kipakin la ka sa'i, Lalpa lopi hen,
 Zie bang Tanpa lopi keia!

[V5]
 4. A vakna a kithuom a ka thawh kit tieng,
 Van mei laka Amah tuok di'n;
 A Hukdamna bukim, A Hehpihna mak,
 Pakcha'n Van mi tawh la sa'ng kau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>88</hymn_number>
</song>